Source: sonic-bmc-platform-aspeed
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Nexthop <opensource@nexthop.ai>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-python, python3-all, python3-setuptools, python3-build
Standards-Version: 3.9.6

Package: sonic-bmc-platform-aspeed-evb
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}
Description: SONiC BMC platform support for Aspeed AST2700 EVB
 This package provides platform-specific implementation for Aspeed AST2700
 EVB (Evaluation Board). It inherits from the common base classes (installed
 in the pmon Docker image) and provides EVB-specific configurations and overrides.

Package: sonic-bmc-platform-aspeed-nexthop
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}
Description: SONiC BMC platform support for NextHop Aspeed AST2700 BMC
 This package provides platform-specific implementation for NextHop's
 Aspeed AST2700 BMC platform. It inherits from the common base classes
 (installed in the pmon Docker image) and provides NextHop-specific
 configurations, USB networking support, and switch CPU utilities.
 Supports multiple card revisions with runtime detection.
